   291→// handleFree godoc
   292→// @summary
   293→// @tags free
   294→// @description This endpoint allows the users to free the Buffers from the
   295→// metric store. This endpoint offers the users to remove then systematically
   296→// and also allows then to prune the data under node, if they do not want to
   297→// remove the whole node.
   298→// @produce     json
   299→// @param       to        query    string        false  "up to timestamp"
